data.description: Completely remodeled inside and out! This outstanding home is fresh on the market offering 5 bedrooms, 3 baths, spacious rooms and offering open concept. You will love the new kitchen with white cabinets, farm sink, walk in pantry, new stainless steel appliances. White woodwork throughout! Step down into the master bedroom and bath offering double sinks, tiled shower, barn doors and laundry closet. There are two additional bedrooms on the main level and two bedroom on the upper level.... Lots of room for office, bonus room, craft room, etc. The sunroom is 30x18 and offers a gas stove and this is not included in Sq footage.. Oh, so much room! The roof and front porch are brand new..Low maintence with new windows and attic insulation !
